### Online Library System — API Test Requests
### Requires the "REST Client" VS Code extension (humao.rest-client)
### Click "Send Request" above any block below once your backend is running.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE_AFTER_LOGIN

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register a new member
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Log in as seeded admin
# Copy the "token" from the response and paste it into @token above
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@library.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Get my profile (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/books

### Search books
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?search=clean&genre=Technology

### Get one book by ID (replace with a real ID from the list above)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/PASTE_BOOK_ID_HERE

### Create a book (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "The Hobbit",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "isbn": "9780547928227",
  "genre": "Fiction",
  "description": "A hobbit's unexpected journey.",
  "totalCopies": 3,
  "publishedYear": 1937
}

### Borrow a book (replace with a real book ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/borrow/PASTE_BOOK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### My borrow history
GET {{baseUrl}}/borrow/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Return a book (replace with a real borrow record ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/borrow/PASTE_BORROW_ID_HERE/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### All borrow records (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/borrow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
